	('2026-03-26 16:14:24.004413+00', 'Reality Queens – auf High Heels durch den Dschungel', 'High heels on, glamor off: In the new reality series, 12 well-known reality contestants trek through the jungle of the greenest country in the world: Suriname. But they don''t know exactly where they are going until they leave.', 'Reality', 'active', '2026-03-26 16:14:24.17+00', 'ed49effa-891f-453f-8e80-961d224b1525', 'reality-queens-auf-high-heels-durch-den-dschungel-2024', '256321', 'reality-queens-auf-high-heels-durch-den-dschungel', 'Reality Queens', NULL, NULL, NULL),
