	('2026-03-26 16:14:22.815538+00', 'Love Island: Hot Flirts & True Love', 'On Love Island, a group of candidates called "Islander" live isolated from the outside world in a villa on Mallorca (Tenerife in spring 2021), under constant observation by video cameras. In order to stay in the villa, one must be linked to another "Islander", whether it is for love, friendship is the basis or for calculation (the couple remaining at the end receives 50,000 euros in prize money).', 'Reality', 'active', '2026-03-26 16:14:22.98+00', 'b3c315b5-b757-47ac-a119-3b42cb7e420a', 'love-island-hot-flirts-true-love-2017', '77550', 'love-island-hot-flirts-true-love', 'Love Island', NULL, NULL, NULL),
